Text: nah, I don’t eat anything red when I purge, for that reason. it’s not a ton of blood, it looks like a string that’s about an inch long, and there’s multiple of them

Author: tofu_snob
Text: Are you eating anything that's red? It could be a lot of things, so it might be a good idea to get checked out by a doctor. Perhaps you have a tear in your esophagus which can be incredibly dangerous if it gets worse.
